survey_response.review_text: We visited Dr Deepesh for my 4 year old daughter's tooth problem. Sir is very patient in explaining the problem. Did root canal for two teeths. Because of his friendliness my daughter allowed him to do the procedure. We are very happy with the whole experience and I would recommend anyone who has kid.Before this Clove dental already told me that there is no solution except root canal for all the 8 teeth. We were so worried. But sir took the case so calmly and explained different solution which worked for us very well.
Good explanation of treatment options and outcomes, warm and friendly demeanour, scheduled appointment and on time consultation.

As we came to the right place for my kid dental issues after visiting multiple clinics.My kid was suffering with dental issues and for that we visited many clinics but all of them suggested complex treatment which she cannot cooperate with that.But at Giggles, Dr Deepesh Singh knows how to handle the kids very well.we undergone through 100% painless treatment and my kid is doing well after that.Thank you sir for treating my kid.

review_reply.reply_text: Thank you for taking valuable time out and providing encouragement. friendly , stress free care is our hallmark. We always spend maximum time on understanding your issue and discussing the options before the treatment.happy to help

survey_response.review_text: Dr. Deepesh Singh is awesome dental doctor. He explained us the treatment when we went for our kid dental problems. He made him very comfortable and the dental checking setup is really amazing. Kids will not feel it is a health care setup but as a friendly play area. Dr. Deepesh suggested progressive treatment instead of the extraction which might be problematic.  There is no wait time if you book prior appointment which is very good. Would like to recommend him for any kids dental checkup. His smiling and friendly greeting, always make us comfortable.

Dr Deepesh was very patient and gentle with my 4 yr old. Took time to explain the root of the problem. Ensured my kid was comfortable and he connected well with him.  Did not push anything drastic as first measures which is highly appreciated by us. Found a good dentist in Dr Deepesh for my kid!

We booked for a video consultation, 30 minutes. Doctor arrived on time but spent just 5 minutes before leaving for another work (OT case). I don't understand when I blocked the time for my consultation, how can I not get the full time? Yes, 5 minutes for ~550 Rs. I couldn't get to ask the questions I have prepared because of the rush created. All I was told was don't go for extraction. Later after an hour, the doctor messaged back in WhatsApp and answered couple of questions. Again the same response. I should have thought twice before booking. Disappointed.

**** ** *** **** ********* ******* ******** *** ***** We see Dr. Deepesh and he is so patient with my kiddos. The staff is welcoming and nice, most importantly they help my kids relax and have a good experience at the dentist. The office is so kid friendly and that makes our visits be fun. I feel like they provided a lot useful information in every one of our visits. Dr. Deepesh never rushes us, but always explains what is going on with our kids and what his recommendations are. Highly recommend this practice, specially if you have little ones who are nervous about seeing the dentist.

survey_response.review_text: Me and my wife visited the doctor for cavities and other dental issues. Starting with the environment as the Covid scare is still on! - The team at Giggles make sure that you feel safe during the visit and all the precautions are taken. Dr. Deepesh was extremely helpful and so patient! He made sure all the issues were discussed properly by asking different questions and making sure we did not have any doubts left unanswered. We got the cavities treated and filled and never once felt being rushed (which usually most doctors do!!) Sneha Ma'am helped with tooth cleaning and scaling with great patience and finess. They reach out for regular follow-ups to ensure the treatment is working and if there are any additional questions.Overall extremely satisfied and highly recommend Dr. Deepesh and his team for all kind of dental consulting.

Doctor was very good in explaining the problem and guided us the remedies and procedures to fix it. Environment was friendly so it was very easy to express our thoughts and doubts and get them clarified. Good part was the patient gets sufficient time to discuss about the issue. He makes sure that the patient or guardian is clear about the condition, if not, he clears it patiently. My kid feels comfortable in visiting this dental premises. Kids are handled  with care and gets easily adjusted with the doctor. I would definitely recommend him for pediatric dental issues - Vihanka P

They took complete care of my daughter made her more delight and friendly Before the check up starts. since she is 4 yrs old.

Where ever we visit they take consultation fee etc before they proceed. 
But in giggles they prevent and cure  first.
I would recommend Giggles****** ************ **** ****
Thank you Dipesh sir.
